	<element name="Lunar Crescent Dagger" type="Magic Item" source="JCDM" id="JCDM_Weapon_02">
		<description>
			<p>
				This dagger is shaped like a crescent moon.  The wickedly curved blade is made of mithril and sharpened on both sides.
				The hilt is shaped like a monstrosity from the depths; stylized tentacles reach out from the handle and run along the flat of the blade.
				The pommel is shaped like a ravening maw.  The hilt is wrapped in a deep blue/near black leather.
			</p>
